Package: looplook
Title: Tools for Integrative Analysis of Chromatin Loops and Expression
Version: 0.99.0
Authors@R: 
    person(given = "Ying", family = "Zhang" , email = "12207129@zju.edu.cn", role = c("aut", "cre"), comment = c(ORCID = "0009-0005-9644-7062"))
Description: A comprehensive toolkit for processing HiChIP/Hi-C loops, 
    annotating loop anchors with gene expression data, reclassifying regulatory elements, 
    and generating publication-quality visualizations like flower plots and track plots.
